title: Realistic Tips for a Healthy Marriage Ft. Tori and Chad Masters
description:
It takes a lot to contain a healthy marriage, so our friends, Tori and Chad, came on to share some of their tips on how they continuously work on their marriage.


Want to send Jeanine a message?  You can do that here: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy by clicking "Message."
